reviewText: Huntress is a good movie but it could have been so much better if the filmmakers focused on the werewolf parts and have made it uncut instead of the heavily edited R-rating.  It's a good start.  Maybe they can remake this movie in the near future.  A good movie that could have been so much better and I wished it was.  A hot red-head werewolf runs amok throughout the Welsh countryside!!Strongly recommended.
summary: Good werewolf movie, could have been better.

reviewText: Beware the sinners of Wales! Naked babes in the winecellar! In the shower! (Then eating eggs) On the thepiano! In the Tub! Touching themselves,well,in naughtyplaces! Nudity in a stinking wet cave!(with flashing light)A three-some in an old country house! A sullen butler!(who drives the main character around in a dippy old car)A lousy ending! But all in all, plenty of fun 'n' games inole Britain.(Sequel: "Mucking About in Wales II")or - "Living In Welsh Caves On Five Pounds A Week"

reviewText: This was not very entertaining.  After I looked at the reviews in Amazon,I bought it.  I made a mistake.  I collect dvds, and I am going to give this one away for a joke to someone. There is no real plot, the acting was lacking, and the story did not develop very well. I was left wondering why I bought it.  I have only bought one that was worse, and I threw it in the trash.  People need to review better.
summary: Few movies are worse than this one
